ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v28.segment

Class GP2

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractSegment
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v28.segment.GP2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Segment, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class GP2
extends AbstractSegment

    Represents an HL7 GP2 message segment (Grouping/Reimbursement - Procedure Line Item). This segment has the following fields:

    • GP2-1: Revenue Code (CWE) optional
    • GP2-2: Number of Service Units (NM) optional
    • GP2-3: Charge (CP) optional
    • GP2-4: Reimbursement Action Code (CWE) optional
    • GP2-5: Denial or Rejection Code (CWE) optional
    • GP2-6: OCE Edit Code (CWE) optional repeating
    • GP2-7: Ambulatory Payment Classification Code (CWE) optional
    • GP2-8: Modifier Edit Code (CWE) optional repeating
    • GP2-9: Payment Adjustment Code (CWE) optional
    • GP2-10: Packaging Status Code (CWE) optional
    • GP2-11: Expected CMS Payment Amount (CP) optional
    • GP2-12: Reimbursement Type Code (CWE) optional
    • GP2-13: Co-Pay Amount (CP) optional
    • GP2-14: Pay Rate per Service Unit (NM) optional
    See Also:
